title: 1.14.0 tests fail (1 run-pass, 1 compile-fail) on arm64

labels.name: O-Arm
labels.description: Target: 32-bit Arm processors (armv6, armv7, thumb...), including 64-bit Arm in AArch32 state

body:
We are bootstrapping this from Debian's 1.13.0, see https://buildd.debian.org/status/fetch.php?pkg=rustc&arch=arm64&ver=1.14.0%2Bdfsg1-1&stamp=1482639065&raw=1

~~~~
